‚ÑπÔ∏è What's the retry1 & retry2?
Some subtitles that are mkv incompatible.  If the remux to mkv fails, we simply try again by changing to a mp4 container, to try and save  the subtitles.  If that doesn't work, we send it back through the stack a 2nd time and remove the subtitles.
This is not as targeted as I would like.  Need to compile a list of all offending subtitles so we can target them for extraction or removal more efficiently.
